WindowTitle {DateTime}
WindowSize  64 64

PeriodicTasks
Begin
   Set $Time = (GetOutput {exec date "+%-I:%M:%S %P"} 1 -1)
   Set $Zone = (GetOutput {exec date "+%Z"} 1 -1)
   Set $Date = (GetOutput {exec date "+%a %-d %b"} 1 -1)

   ChangeTitle 1 $Date
   ChangeTitle 2 $Time
   ChangeTitle 3 $Zone
End

Widget 1
Property
 Position 0 0
 Size 64 20
 Font `-sgi-screen-medium-r-normal--12-120-72-72-m-70-iso8859-1`
 Type ItemDraw
 Flags NoReliefString
 Title {}
Main
 Case message of
  SingleClic :
  Begin
  End
End

